text: Erika has really honed in on a sound here that is so confidently her. I can't stop streaming this.
Favorite track: You Can't Always Get What You Want
She is back and sounding more sultry than ever!!!
this is everything i've ever wanted from erika, it's probably my favorite project of hers. soft, lush vocals and downtempo/triphop beats. such a gorgeous aoty!
love seeing her release independently and leaning into her strengths and talent which lays in her own production <3 a sonic landscape to lay on and look at the clouds
Favorite track: You Can't Always Get What You Want
Erika is the queen. Vibe, emotion and cool.
